OL,5, The Wire co-creator David Simon has    
OL,6, asked a judge for leniency when        
OL,7, sentencing a man charged in the drug   
OL,8, death of actor Michael K Williams.     
OL,10,FWilliams, who starred as robber Omar   
OL,11,FLittle in the HBO crime drama, died of 
OL,12,Fan overdose aged 54 in 2021.           
OL,14,FCarlos Macci is one of four men charged
OL,15,Ffor selling Williams the heroin laced  
OL,16,Fwith fentanyl that killed him.         
OL,18,FMacci, 71, pleaded guilty to conspiracy
OL,19,Fto distribute narcotics in April. He is
OL,20,Fexpected to be sentenced this month.   
